vclaim: A photograph shows First Lady Jill Biden deplaning in black patterned hosiery, ankle boots, and a skirt.
title: Is This a Photograph of Jill Biden in ‘Fishnet Stockings’?
subtitle: A picture of 69-year-old First Lady Jill Biden deplaning while wearing 'fishnet stockings' touched off online debate over the appropriateness of her ensemble.
author: David Mikkelson
